{"word":"H5372 - נִרְגָּן - nirgân - neer-gawn' - Talebearer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נִרְגָּן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>nirgân"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>neer-gawn'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Talebearer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"கோள்சொல்லுகிறவன், கோள்காரன் - ஆண்பால்பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to murmur, to complain, to whisper, complainers a backbiter, slander, a talebearer, a backbiter"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From an unused root meaning to <i>roll</i> to pieces; a <i>slanderer: - </i>talebearer, whisperer."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5372 - נִרְגָּן - nirgân - neer-gawn'/5372\">H5372</a>, <a href=\"#/H7279 - רָגַן - râgan - raw-gan'/7279\">H7279</a>"}]}